            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p><span><span><span>The Nepean Seniors Centre offers recreation programs, and social events for adults 50 years of age and over. </span></span></span>Access to our services is through membership or program registration.</p>
<p>The Nepean Seniors Centre offers programs such as fitness, card games, Short Mat Bowling, lessons and more.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Located within the Nepean Seniors Centre, our accessible facilities include:&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li>garden room,&nbsp;</li>
<li>kitchenette,&nbsp;</li>
<li>lounge with fireplace,</li>
<li>multi-purpose rooms.</li>
</ul>
<p><span><span><span><span>For details about hall rentals, pool, athletic centre and arenas, visit the <a href="https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/recreation-facilities/facility-listing/nepean-sportsplex">Nepean Sportsplex page</a>.</span></span></span></span></p>
