<li><a href="https://ottawa.ca/en/residents/facilities/kanata-seniors-centre">Kanata Seniors Centre</a>,&nbsp;2500 Campeau Drive</li>
<li><a href="https://ottawa.ca/en/residents/facilities/nepean-seniors-recreation-centre">Nepean Seniors Recreation Centre</a>,&nbsp;1701 Woodroffe Avenue</li>
